				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Top 10 Bard Issues compiled<a name="50428"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 7 04 1:11 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I've compiled a list of the Top 10 issues cited by bards in the previous thread here: <a target="_new" href="http://www.eqdiva.com/Forums/ShowPost.aspx?PostID=49809">Post your top bard issues here.</a>
<br />

<br />
I've just tallied the issues mentioned by each person, although it happens to be pretty close to my opinion, too. Next to each issue the number in parentheses counts the number of people who mentioned that particular issue.
<br />

<br />
As of the latest post (8:01 pm PST, July 6), the tally is as follows:
<br />

<br />
1) Fizzle rates (22) - This was fairly evenly divided people people complaining about fizzle rates at max skill (7), at lower levels (5), and ineffectiveness of Casting Focus/Internal Metronome AAs (7).
<br />

<br />
2) Weapon procs &amp; casting bar (10)
<br />

<br />
3) Song pulses &amp; drops on the same tick (9)
<br />

<br />
4) Instrument modifier caps (5) - Not everybody specified whether they wanted the caps raised or eliminated (and the AAs refunded), but I'd assume the latter.
<br />

<br />
5) DoT stacking (4)
<br />

<br />
5) Better group invisibility w/ improved duration &amp; range (4)
<br />

<br />
7) More items w/ instrument modifiers (3) - One person specified that he'd like more 1.8+ mods, specifically, to reduce reliance on the epic.
<br />

<br />
7) Increase movement cap (3) - This includes complaints about Fleet of Foot.
<br />

<br />
7) Targetting issues post-DX9 (3)
<br />

<br />
Due to the small sample size, there is a 7-way tie for the tenth slot. In no particular order:
<br />

<br />
10) Make songs auto-stop when a new song begins to eliminate double-tapping (2)
<br />

<br />
10) Twisting problems post-DX9 (2)
<br />

<br />
10) Increase melee damage mitigation (2)
<br />

<br />
10) Create hotkeys for instrument-swapping (2)
<br />

<br />
10) Give us more varied songs in OoW (2)
<br />

<br />
10) AE songs overwritten by bards with lower cap (2)
<br />

<br />
10) Make lockpick better/more useful (2)
<br />

<br />
I've left off this list any issue that only one person brought up. I'm trying to leave my own personal opinions out of this because I admit that I'm just a low-level bard who doesn't have the slightest clue what some of you uber folks do in Time or GoD while I'm crawling through LDoNs. I'm just doing this tally because, well, somebody's gotta do the work. (And I think Tremelo has enough going as it is.)
<br />

<br />
I'll update this if/when others post.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
