<br />

<br />
It is just a pain to keep looking at my window for all the missed notes, can't see target msgs, out of range, and having to stop any song to click an item.
<br />

<br />
------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
We need an upgraded invis song with 3x the range post 50. I have never used my invis for group travel since level 30 due to how bad it is. For self invis it works great.
<br />

<br />
I think bards stack well in a raid, I have never had too many bards.  In theory we lack stackability, but since we are so few there never seems to be that problem.
<br />

<br />
------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
If you look at the bard songs 1-50, I really like how they were designed, they got stronger as you progressed, and you got new abilities almost each level.  
<br />

<br />
This was very nice, as the casters were more poorly designed with a base spell class and each level rank they recieved power boosts to the same spell with a different name.
<br />

<br />
With the expansions, they lost creativity and we got pretty much two new songs (not power boosts) DA song, and teleport to bind song.
<br />

<br />
I know it is too much to ask to see new songs that are not only upgrades, but I can always hope.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
