				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Top 10 Bard Issues compiled<a name="50612"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 7 04 8:18 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>1) Instrument modifier caps - the caps eliminated. Like someone else pointed out there is no reason for these to hold us back if we get a new nice instrument. No other class has to deal with such a restriction.
<br />

<br />
2) DoT stacking - again no other class is restricted by this!
<br />

<br />
3) Fizzle rates - this one doesn't bother me too much until i recieve like 5 fizzles in a row and I feel like I am lvl 10 again!!
<br />

<br />
4) More items w/ instrument modifiers 1.8+ - This would be awsome, I loved getting my epic but its crappy ratio is part of the reason bard melee sucks. next point!
<br />

<br />
5) Increase melee damage mitigation - just a little, its not class defining or anything but just a little would be nice.
<br />

<br />
6) Agro builder - maybe give us taunt again(warriors say it sucks now anyway) an agro song something! It would be nice to save a caster with a quick agro just once or twice.
<br />

<br />
7) Increase movement cap - sure why not.
<br />

<br />
8) Give us more varied songs in OoW - sounds good to me.</span></td>
